Let 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 be nonsingular, and suppose 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{x}\neq0$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{b}\neq0$
\end_inset

.
 Then
